dct_description_sm: Andalusia section of southern Spain. Latin and Spanish. "Privilegio Imp. et Regis maesti." Pictorial relief. Latin text on verso with caption title: Hispalensis conventus, sive Andaluziae pars; p. 18. Probably issued in: Theatrum orbis terrarum ... Antverpiae : Plantin, 1592. This map was used in Latin editions of the Theatrum from 1592 to 1609. cf. Broecke, M.P.R. van den. Ortelius atlas maps.
